data.description: This stunning, 3bed/3bath home in the gated SPI Golf Community comes fully furnished. Enjoy your large backyard oasis w/ heated saltwater pool (heater 2021), lush landscaping, covered patio and vinyl fence. Plenty of space and privacy--perfect for entertaining. This chef's kitchen boasts a center island, granite counters, decorative backsplash, stainless steel appliances, touch screen refrigerator & a pantry. Two primary suites with walk-in closets. The large driveway and 2 car garage provides plenty of parking. Shelving, a refrigerator and utility sink are an added bonus. This home has an open floor plan, plenty of storage, tile throughout, dual pane windows, ceiling fans and so much more!
